title: Swift Security v1.4.2.6 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
With the Swift Security plugin you can make your Wordpress website more secure with a single click. A great advantage of the plugin is that you don't need any special technical knowledge. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
